#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/grimlock.md:11
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Armor Class** 11    \n"
"**Hit Points** 11 (2d8 + 2)    \n"
"**Speed** 30 ft. \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/grimlock.md:15
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"| STR     | DEX     | CON     | INT     | WIS     | CHA     |\n"
"|---------|---------|---------|---------|---------|---------|\n"
"| 16 (+3) | 12 (+1) | 12 (+1) | 9 (−1)  | 8 (−1)  | 6 (−2)  |\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/grimlock.md:21
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Skills** Athletics +5, Perception +3, Stealth +3    \n"
"**Condition Immunities** blinded    \n"
"**Senses** blindsight 30 ft. or 10 ft. while deafened (blind beyond this "
"radius), passive Perception 13    \n"
"**Languages** Undercommon    \n"
"**Challenge** 1/4 (50 XP)    \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/grimlock.md:25
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Blind Senses**. The grimlock can't use its blindsight while deafened and "
"unable to smell.    \n"
"**Keen Hearing and Smell.** The grimlock has advantage on Wisdom "
"(Perception) checks that rely on hearing or smell.    \n"
"**Stone Camouflage.** The grimlock has advantage on Dexterity (Stealth) "
"checks made to hide in rocky terrain. \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/grimlock.md:27
msgid ""
"### Actions **Spiked Bone Club.** _Melee Weapon Attack:_ +5 to hit, reach 5 "
"ft., one target. _Hit:_ 5 (1d4 + 3) bludgeoning damage plus 2 (1d4) piercing "
"damage."
msgstr ""
